The chakalaka South African taste, a little spicy and full of flavour.  Chakalaka Chicken  Easy Meals for busy people 1.5kg chicken pieces (thighs and drumsticks) Salt and pepper 1 can chakalaka 1/2 cup mayonnaise 1 tsp brown sugar 1/2 cup yoghurt 4 tbsp flour 1/2 cup chicken stock  Method Heat oven to 180Â°C Sprinkle salt and pepper on to chicken pieces. Place the chicken in an ovenproof dish. Mix the remaining ingredients together, pour over the chicken and place in the oven for 40 minutes. Cooking time may vary according to the size of the chicken pieces. Serve with rice or salad. Easy! The Saturday Star